title: Wildfire: The Story of Horse (1945) Color Western Classic | Full Length Movie

sources.title: Wildfire: The Story of Horse (1945) Color Western Classic | Full Length Movie
sources.description:
Guns Roared Amid Thundering Hoofs as the Law and a WILD HORSE brought peace and order to a Horse Rustling country!
Two horse-traders (Bob Steele, Sterling Holloway) find their problem is a rustler (John Miljan), not a wild horse.

Director: Robert Emmett Tansey
Writers: W.C. Tuttle, Frances Kavanaugh
Stars: Bob Steele, Sterling Holloway, John Miljan
